Simon Says - AngularJS
----------------------------------

This web application uses AngularJS, an MVC framework, and BonsaiJS, a simple animation framework, to implement a version of the Simon Says game. 

Running the application:

To run this application, open gameStart.html in your browser (prefferably Chrome or Firefox) by entering this path into the URL: 
file:///YourDrive:/SimonSaysAngular/gameStart.html